title: League Of Legends "Launch" does nothing
body: Two days ago, I was logging onto League and it took a good minute to show the log in screen, which, isn't normal for me. Despite this, I didn't care much for it but yesterday and today it got worse. It would't work  at all. I could hear the sound but nothing happened, and I've tried redownloading, deleting lol_patcher and lol_airclient and I've tried changing DNS. I couldn't even repair and when I did nothing happened. Any help would be great but I'd like to fix this before the Captain Gangplank skin leaves and the mystery OPL skin comes. Thanks!  {{champion:222}}

replies.body: I saw something about "thereisnourflevel", can I use that to log on?
